question: Question: Working titles for this movie include Anhedonia, It Had to Be Jew, Me and My Goy, and Rollercoaster Named Desire.  [10] Identify this 1977 Best Picture Oscar winner, a romantic comedy which chronicles the relationship between the comedian Alvy Singer and the title character, played by Diane Keaton.
